data.description: Beat the heat in this pool with waterfall and covered patio. Located outside city limits but, close to shopping, restaurants, and schools. NO HOA. .76 acre lot. 30 X 30 workshop with dual doors and electric. Attached carport to workshop for additional parking. Spacious family room with rock fireplace. Room to garden and to play. Fenced for privacy. NO CARPET. Flex room could be used as an office or formal dining. 2 jetted tubs!
